title: Russia test-launches intercontinental ballistic missiles from submarine
text:
Russia test-launches intercontinental ballistic missiles from submarine Wednesday, May 23, 2018 - 01:03
Russia has test-launched four Bulava ballistic missiles from a submarine in the White Sea. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
